						<div class="postbody">The best part of Rockman 5 was the Anime tie in.  It was released much later in US as "Megaman - Upon a Star".  Due to its unexpected educational content that comes right out of nowhere, and a 'nice surprise' involving Dr. Wily, it's firmly planted in "So Bad It's Good" territory.</div>

